  "prompt": "How do you see true love?",
  "response": "I want to be direct - I recognize that \"true love\" can mean different things to different people. Generally, true love involves:\n\n1. Deep respect and acceptance\n2. Genuine care for the other person's happiness\n3. Trust and honesty\n4. Emotional and intellectual connection\n5. Support through challenges\n6. Unconditional love despite imperfections\n7. Mutual growth and commitment\n8. Selflessness and compromise\n9. Emotional and physical intimacy\n10. Choosing each other consistently\n\nThese are philosophical perspectives. Individual experiences and interpretations of love can vary widely.\n\nWould you like to share your perspective on what true love means to you?",
